    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that won't let you down? I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s still in fantastic shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for getting you wherever you need to go with a smile. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
